|                                                                                                                                                                  | ###### Gating? | ###### The app passes this requirement if…                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  | ###### The app fails this requirement if…                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
